- Python 3.12 virtualenv
- Django 5.2.2 as backend framework (no Flask, no FastAPI)
- PostgreSQL as DB via psycopg2-binary
- Pillow for images
- django-mptt (+ admin) for nested/tree categories
- stripe for payment integration (BLIK + Przelewy24 should be available)
- django-turnstile for forms protection 
- python-dotenv for .env config/secrets
- **Custom SCSS/SASS only** for styles (no Tailwind, Bootstrap, or CSS frameworks unless we find a good use case)
  - All SCSS source files live in `static/scss/`
  - SCSS is compiled using **Dart Sass** (`npm install sass`) via npm scripts
  - Compiled CSS output goes to `static/css/`
  - Reference CSS in templates via `{% static 'css/style.css' %}`
- JS is vanilla/handwritten unless specified
- No frontend JS/CSS frameworks unless project requirements change
- All templates are Django template language (not Jinja2, not React)
- Follow Django app/project conventions for file paths and structure